6747
03:58:32,579 --> 03:58:34,379
He glanced at peril.

6748
03:58:34,440 --> 03:58:36,299
Lots of papers everywhere.

6749
03:58:36,360 --> 03:58:38,760
I'll wait here.

6750
03:58:38,819 --> 03:58:40,559
Parel said sadly.

6751
03:58:40,680 --> 03:58:43,260
She drew her tail in close to herself

6752
03:58:43,260 --> 03:58:45,719
leaving a moon shaped swath in the sand.

6753
03:58:45,780 --> 03:58:49,379
Lead on, Thorn said to Smolder.

6754
03:58:49,440 --> 03:58:51,899
Sonny joined them, and they headed into

6755
03:58:51,899 --> 03:58:53,879
yet another twisting set of corridors.

6756
03:58:53,940 --> 03:58:56,280
These ones lined with flickering diamond

6757
03:58:56,280 --> 03:58:58,440
shaped mirrors that caught the sunlight

6758
03:58:58,440 --> 03:59:00,299
from small holes in the roof and walls.

6759
