I don't hate all night wings.

6768
03:59:20,219 --> 03:59:21,959
Thorn said quietly.

6769
03:59:22,020 --> 03:59:25,379
I mean, I'm not fond of them, and I don't

6770
03:59:25,379 --> 03:59:27,600
trust them as a rule, but I'm looking for

6771
03:59:27,600 --> 03:59:30,479
