Sonny guessed.

6775
03:59:35,219 --> 03:59:36,000
Is that why?

6776
03:59:36,059 --> 03:59:38,159
Not exactly.

6777
03:59:38,219 --> 03:59:41,879
Well, I guess in a manner of speaking

6778
03:59:41,879 --> 03:59:43,200
Thorn said.

6779
03:59:43,319 --> 03:59:45,600
Glancing up at the skylights with an odd

6780
03:59:45,600 --> 03:59:48,899
half smile, Sonny stared at her, she had

6781
