regular sandwing, Thorn said.

6785
03:59:58,500 --> 04:00:03,239
So, it's because Sonny's claws trembled

6786
04:00:03,239 --> 04:00:06,000
with shock of all the theories she'd ever

6787
04:00:06,000 --> 04:00:06,540
imagined.

6788
04:00:06,600 --> 04:00:09,719
Yes, this one had crossed her mind, but

6789
04:00:09,719 --> 04:00:11,700
of all the tribes she'd wondered about

6790
04:00:11,700 --> 04:00:12,659
never this one.

6791
04:00:12,780 --> 04:00:15,420
Never, never this one.

6792
04:00:15,479 --> 04:00:18,360
Yes, sonny, said Thorn.

6793
04:00:18,420 --> 04:00:20,819
Her voice falling like drops of water

6794
04:00:20,819 --> 04:00:22,379
