6795
04:00:22,379 --> 04:00:25,020
It's because you're half night wing.

6796
04:00:25,079 --> 04:00:29,399
Chapter 14.

6797
04:00:29,579 --> 04:00:33,780
But the night wings are awful, Sonny

6798
04:00:33,780 --> 04:00:34,620
