6814
04:01:05,940 --> 04:01:09,959
Half night wing by all the moons.

6815
04:01:10,020 --> 04:01:11,879
Please tell me about him.

6816
04:01:11,940 --> 04:01:13,379
I want to know everything.

6817
04:01:13,440 --> 04:01:15,059
