6818
04:01:15,120 --> 04:01:15,959
Do I?

6819
04:01:16,020 --> 04:01:18,479
How did you fall in love with a night

6820
04:01:18,479 --> 04:01:19,860
wing of all the tribes?

6821
04:01:19,920 --> 04:01:22,799
Thorn folded her wings back and ducked

6822
04:01:22,799 --> 04:01:23,700
under a low archway.

6823
04:01:23,760 --> 04:01:27,479
Eight years ago, I met a dragon, out in

6824
04:01:27,479 --> 04:01:28,860
the sands not far from here, actually.

6825
04:01:28,920 --> 04:01:31,739
His scales were like the desert sky at

6826
04:01:31,739 --> 04:01:34,379
night, and he was always nervous in a

6827
04:01:34,379 --> 04:01:36,899
sweet, worried way, like no other dragon

6828
04:01:36,899 --> 04:01:37,559
