6842
04:02:04,559 --> 04:02:07,379
If she was like her mother, did that mean

6843
04:02:07,379 --> 04:02:09,059
she would end up in love with a dragon

6844
04:02:09,059 --> 04:02:10,200
who was like her father?

6845
04:02:10,260 --> 04:02:11,879
Was that her type?

6846
04:02:12,000 --> 04:02:13,979
Was that her destiny?

6847
04:02:14,040 --> 04:02:16,440
Her and Starflight together?

6848
04:02:16,500 --> 04:02:19,440
She had many thoughts about that, but no

6849
04:02:19,440 --> 04:02:20,579
idea how to sort them out.

6850
04:02:20,639 --> 04:02:25,079
He gave me this, Thorn said, touching the

6851
04:02:25,079 --> 04:02:26,159
