6852
04:02:26,280 --> 04:02:29,280
I asked him why he was here, and he said

6853
04:02:29,280 --> 04:02:30,600
he was trying to save his tribe.

6854
04:02:30,659 --> 04:02:32,520
I liked that too.

6855
04:02:32,579 --> 04:02:33,959
She went on.

6856
04:02:34,020 --> 04:02:36,719
He really, really cared about saving his

6857
04:02:36,719 --> 04:02:37,379
tribe.

6858
04:02:37,440 --> 04:02:40,379
I'd never seen loyalty before because

6859
04:02:40,379 --> 04:02:42,239
there was nothing like the outlaws back

6860
04:02:42,239 --> 04:02:44,280
then, not in the scorpion den.

6861
04:02:44,340 --> 04:02:46,319
He said he was doing something essential

6862
04:02:46,319 --> 04:02:47,760
