6863
04:02:47,819 --> 04:02:50,819
Oh, Sonny gasped.

6864
04:02:50,879 --> 04:02:51,959
The tunnels.

6865
04:02:52,020 --> 04:02:53,879
He must be the animus who built the

6866
04:02:53,879 --> 04:02:54,299
tunnels.

6867
04:02:54,360 --> 04:02:56,700
Thorn looked at her curiously.

6868
04:02:56,760 --> 04:02:57,959
You know about that?

6869
04:02:58,020 --> 04:03:01,680
Wait, tunnels, as in multiple tunnels?

6870
04:03:01,739 --> 04:03:04,319
Two of them, Sonny said.

6871
04:03:04,379 --> 04:03:06,840
As far as I know, those are the only ones

6872
04:03:06,840 --> 04:03:07,920
I've been through anyway.

6873
04:03:07,979 --> 04:03:12,360
You have been around, Thorn said. with a

6874
04:03:12,360 --> 04:03:13,739
hint of admiration in her voice.

6875
04:03:13,799 --> 04:03:16,200
