6876
04:03:16,260 --> 04:03:19,260
He was here every day for a while, trying

6877
04:03:19,260 --> 04:03:21,420
to pick the right spot and working of the

6878
04:03:21,420 --> 04:03:22,379
energy to create it.

6879
