6895
04:04:00,239 --> 04:04:04,319
No one knew, except Six Claws and my

6896
04:04:04,319 --> 04:04:06,600
friend Armadillo, Thorn admitted.

6897
04:04:06,659 --> 04:04:09,659
Stone Mover was my secret.

6898
04:04:09,719 --> 04:04:11,459
Of course, I didn't have a whole lot of

6899
04:04:11,459 --> 04:04:12,360
