6902
04:04:18,180 --> 04:04:20,879
Thorn stepped in front of Sonny?

6903
04:04:20,940 --> 04:04:22,680
and put up her wings to stop her in

6904
04:04:22,680 --> 04:04:22,979
place.

6905
04:04:23,040 --> 04:04:24,659
