6907
04:04:25,680 --> 04:04:28,139
I don't tell everyone about my past

6908
04:04:28,139 --> 04:04:30,600
because I like my privacy, and there

6909
04:04:30,600 --> 04:04:32,040
isn't much of that when you lead a band

6910
04:04:32,040 --> 04:04:32,819
of outlaws.

6911
04:04:32,879 --> 04:04:35,579
But I'm not ashamed of you, or of where

6912
04:04:35,579 --> 04:04:36,540
