6923
04:04:59,700 --> 04:05:00,479
You understand?

6924
04:05:00,600 --> 04:05:02,639
Sonny nodded.

6925
04:05:02,700 --> 04:05:04,860
She thought Dragon should be allowed to

6926
04:05:04,860 --> 04:05:07,079
love whoever they fell in love with, but

6927
04:05:07,079 --> 04:05:08,459
at the same time, she couldn't help

6928
04:05:08,459 --> 04:05:10,379
thinking, look at me though.

6929
04:05:10,440 --> 04:05:14,639
No natural weapons, no powers, scales

6930
04:05:14,639 --> 04:05:16,500
