6931
04:05:16,559 --> 04:05:19,260
I'm kind of a walking argument for

6932
04:05:19,260 --> 04:05:21,719
avoiding intertribe relationships, aren't

6933
04:05:21,719 --> 04:05:21,840
I?

6934
04:05:21,959 --> 04:05:24,540
Her mother looked as if she could read

6935
04:05:24,540 --> 04:05:26,040
Sonny's thoughts on her face.

6936
04:05:26,100 --> 04:05:28,860
She brushed her front talons over Sunny's

6937
04:05:28,860 --> 04:05:30,959
