Sonny, you are perfect.

6939
04:05:33,479 --> 04:05:34,620
The way you are.

6940
04:05:34,680 --> 04:05:37,680
So what happened to stone mover.

6941
04:05:37,739 --> 04:05:38,700
Sonny asked.

6942
04:05:38,760 --> 04:05:40,739
She didn't want to think about her weird

6943
04:05:40,739 --> 04:05:42,899
looks anymore, at least for a little

6944
04:05:42,899 --> 04:05:43,139
while.

6945
04:05:43,200 --> 04:05:44,879
He disappeared.

6946
04:05:44,940 --> 04:05:48,239
Thorn let go of her, and blew out a

6947
04:05:48,239 --> 04:05:49,739
breath with hints of fire in it.

6948
04:05:49,799 --> 04:05:52,260
I came back one day and he was gone.

6949
04:05:52,319 --> 04:05:55,200
Morrow seer was there instead.

6950
04:05:55,319 --> 04:05:58,260
He said it was my fault, whatever had

6951
04:05:58,260 --> 04:06:00,479
happened to Stone Mover, and never to

6952
04:06:00,479 --> 04:06:01,860
look for him or try to speak to him

6953
04:06:01,860 --> 04:06:02,159
again.

6954
04:06:02,219 --> 04:06:05,639
Pompous, worm faced, snobhead camel

6955
04:06:05,639 --> 04:06:06,120
turd.

6956
04:06:06,239 --> 04:06:07,799
Mother!

6957
04:06:07,860 --> 04:06:10,079
Sonny said, nearly shocked into

6958
04:06:10,079 --> 04:06:10,500
laughing.

6959
04:06:10,559 --> 04:06:14,040
That's what he was, Thorn growled.

6960
04:06:14,100 --> 04:06:15,479
Morrow seer.

6961
04:06:15,540 --> 04:06:18,120
I dream about wringing his neck all the

6962
04:06:18,120 --> 04:06:18,420
time.

6963
04:06:18,479 --> 04:06:21,780
She sighed, and her claws scratched

6964
04:06:21,780 --> 04:06:23,040
across the stone as if they were

6965
04:06:23,040 --> 04:06:24,059
frustrated too.

6966
04:06:24,120 --> 04:06:26,879
We didn't like him much either, Sonny

6967
