6992
04:07:14,760 --> 04:07:17,879
gotten very strange and cold, so maybe he

6993
04:07:17,879 --> 04:07:18,420
wasn't going to.

6994
04:07:18,479 --> 04:07:21,899
That's what happens to animus dragons

6995
04:07:21,899 --> 04:07:22,739
Sonny said.

6996
04:07:22,799 --> 04:07:25,620
Whenever they use their magic, they lose

6997
04:07:25,620 --> 04:07:27,299
a little bit of their soul or something

6998
04:07:27,299 --> 04:07:27,719
like that.

